songs.title: Magic Fever
songs.lyrics:
Put your headphones
And remember what you've got
Turn the TV Off
And play Bertrand Burgarat

Shut the lights to see your silouette at night
Unplug the phone and free your mind

Surrender!

Let's give a rest to your underwear
And let me know what kind of wine would you prefer
After your bubblebath I will never forget
The nice sound of waves breaking at the surf

Surrender!

Put your headphones
And remember............
